sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant QE as QueryEngine
    participant QL as queryLoop
    participant API as 模型API
    participant Tools as 工具层

    User->>QE: submitMessage(prompt)
    QE->>QE: processUserInput + recordTranscript
    QE->>QL: for await (query(...))

    QL->>API: callModel(messages)
    API-->>QL: stream_event(message_start)
    API-->>QL: stream_event(content_block)
    API-->>QL: stream_event(message_delta stop_reason=tool_use)
    QL-->>QE: yield assistant消息
    QE->>QE: mutableMessages.push + turnCount追踪

    QL->>Tools: 执行工具调用
    Tools-->>QL: 工具结果
    QL-->>QE: yield user消息(工具结果)

    QL->>QL: 检查maxTurns
    QL->>QL: state = next(turnCount+1)
    QL->>API: callModel(messages+工具结果)
    Note over QL,API: 下一轮循环开始
